Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry! Kerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.27,0:00:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:00:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where this island's name comes from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't Arimago the word for a type of crab?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this was a place where they made offerings to the sea gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a girl, with nothing to feed her sick mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,took some of the food that had been offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the girl was cursed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and transformed into a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the name comes from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an awful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shrine where they worshipped those gods
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stood where your mansion now is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,up on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why none of the villagers want to go up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say it's bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you go there too often, you'll be cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They try to scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel like an outsider anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the village, they treat you like my little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really settled in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you first arrived, everyone used to bully you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a weird name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who starting using it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why call me "Kerry"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because your name's really hard to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry... Kerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerytugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even close...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, is that new?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my hundredth success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These flowers never wither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've altered the flow of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never grow beyond this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll also never wither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whether we can get the same theory to work on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first success!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley's been following in my footsteps while she helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She does have talent as a magus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, didn't you do most of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only helped a little at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's still amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I try the thing that Shirley did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had some help, you could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only let Shirley try it because I think she has the necessary knowledge and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, why won't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone just misunderstands him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shirley...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go back to that mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad should spend time with the villagers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father Simon really doesn't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He preaches at me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He claims if I keep working there,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a demon will possess me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to keep it nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says that it's a powerful talisman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you scared of my dad, Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, magical research isn't exactly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the things that he's uncovering could make history!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sharp and easy to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a flower bloom forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is an amazing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley, you did it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Working with flowers is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can do a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His medicines could eradicate human mortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to use his power for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they'll understand how impressive he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's given up on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Kerry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're his best student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone were to do it, it'd be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not his student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most I can be is his assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helping him with little things...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not his student or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even when the priest lectures me about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're his heir, without doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything he's working on,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he plans for you to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a little too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of adult do you want to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take up your dad's work,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what will you use it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a power that could change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And someday, it'll be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't enter my workshop last night, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't go to the village today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley's late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only wanted to prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His research...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that.{We'll have to use *that*.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there'll still be time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold it back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Was that really Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerry, stay here for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go inform the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father Simon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you worry about yourself first?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you just sit there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll join them soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burning down the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you've heard of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call them Dead Apostles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead Apostles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They drink blood to reproduce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly everyone on this island is one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're cleaning it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two groups of people down there who are trying to eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is the Church's Executors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who never doubt that you may slaughter anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who defies the will of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, they'll show no mercy to any Dead Apostles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll kill anyone they even suspect of having had their blood sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's the Magus Association...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they're harder to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd like to keep the secret of who made
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something bizarre like the Dead Apostles all to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsurprisingly, considering they vow to keep everything to themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll kill anyone they suspect of knowing the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll do anything to cover up what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who burned the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like a salesman for the Magus Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a magus who's been marked for sealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that doesn't mean anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first person to become a Dead Apostle here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you could say the medium that made them a Dead Apostle...{means by which?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What caused them to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The renegade magus who made it should be hiding somewhere on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kiritsugu... You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to go to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you researching the Dead Apostles?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu, how did you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.12,0:18:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirley used the magic on herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unwittingly, Shirley showed me the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you use me one day like you used Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dead Apostle that can't control its bloodlust is a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Emiya family research requires unlimited time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akasha will never be attained with a mortal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a time-consuming experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems to have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to rewrite my theory from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiritsugu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll discuss this another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to run now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we run?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hid a motorboat on the south coast,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just in case something like this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kiritsugu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have time to let you gather your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a barrier around the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take time to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kerry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what kind of adult do you want to be when you grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to break that barrier fairly easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only luck that you arrived in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had this man escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'd have continued his Dead Apostles research elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a terrible reason for a kid to kill his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you off the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can decide the rest for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to take anything with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:47.41,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The stars twinkle away silently to their deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:54.91,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\blur2}Heaven and Earth overflow with unanswered prayers
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.91,type,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(640,248)}{21:54}Episode 18: \NDistant Memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:09.51,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}The future glitters on the branch, yet unbloomed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:17.06,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Still reluctant, it slowly unfolds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:24.44,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Behold, the golden apple has ripened and is ready
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:32.45,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}But pick it and the world will end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:47.26,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Just as the falling snow is so pure that it vanishes at the slightest warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:54.31,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}A single beautiful dream tore apart your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:23:02.36,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}and destroyed the kindness in your cold eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:09.78,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Look at the violently twinkling stars disobeying the heavens
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:23.75,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,974)\blur2}Not stopping till they destroy the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After leaving the island, I spent the next several years
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Natalia Kaminski, the woman who took me from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meant choosing the same path as Natalia,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.81,0:23:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the path of a hunter.
